U.S. BANK, N.A., as Legal Title Trustee for Truman 2013 SC4 Title Trust, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Lubica VILCEKOVA, Defendant-Petitioner,
and
Mr. Vilcekova, Husband of Lubica Vilcekova, Howard K. Pfeffer, Esq., and Forest Junction Condominium Association, Defendants. C-557 September Term 2017
078878 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 2, 2018 **145To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005575-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

**146It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
